        "subject": "LU-0000 osc: remove faulty assert in blocking ast",
        "message": "LU-0000 osc: remove faulty assert in blocking ast\n\nIf the OSC is inactivated, the lock enqueue will fail immediately and\nosc_lock::ols_lock will be assigned to dlmlock. The assertion in\nosc_lock_blocking() is wrong in this case.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ia9788dc01e8e51ec20c21e1acf3fb765d0785c4a\n"
      },
